::Rex::

Rex frowns, looking at Battera.

"If Voluis is a normal Predacon, he would gladly sacrifice a bot to destroy 
the Maximal commander."

His words sounded a bit unsure. The visit from Voluis had confused him, and 
he was tempted to believe the ex-Predacon's words. His strong feelings 
against the Predacons interfered with that, however, and Rex was in a state 
of indicition.
